me":"Lua’s Prey: Baruuk Prime: Hotfix 32.2.8","date":"2022-12-15T21:32:58Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1335111-lua%E2%80%99s-prey-baruuk-prime-hotfix-3228/","additions":"","changes":"Lua’S Prey: Baruuk Prime: Hotfix 32.2.8:","fixes":""},{"name":"Lua’s Prey: Baruuk Prime: Hotfix 32.2.7","date":"2022-12-15T19:50:01Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1335045-lua%E2%80%99s-prey-baruuk-prime-hotfix-3227/","additions":"","changes":"Lua’S Prey: Baruuk Prime: Hotfix 32.2.7:","fixes":"Fixed Baruuk not gaining Energy from Energy Restores while Serene Storm is active. \nFixed offset issues with the Embolist Leg Growths Armor and Galvanik Leg Plates when equipped on Baruuk Prime. \nFixed Baruuk’s Elude deactivate sound FX not always playing. "},{"name":"Lua’s Prey: Baruuk Prime: Hotfix 32.2.6","date":"2022-12-14T22:31:43Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1334920-lua%E2%80%99s-prey-baruuk-prime-hotfix-3226/","additions":"","changes":"Lua’S Prey: Baruuk Prime: Hotfix 32.2.6:","fixes":"Fixed offset issues with the Ransha Prime Shoulder Plates when equipped on Baruuk Prime. "},{"name":"Lua’s Prey: Baruuk Prime: Hotfix 32.2.5","date":"2022-12-14T19:00:16Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1334887-lua%E2%80%99s-prey-baruuk-prime-hotfix-3225/","additions":"","changes":"Lua’S Prey: Baruuk Prime: Hotfix 32.2.5:\nPatience gives way to unleashed fury in Baruuk Prime Access! Instantly add the latest Prime Warframe, his signature Prime Weapons and exclusive Prime Accessories to your Arsenal for a limited time.\nPunish those who test your restraint. The first strike in a combo stuns enemies when Cobra & Crane Prime are wielded by Baruuk.\nExclusive Baruuk Prime Glyphs\nBaruuk Prime Mandala\nNow that Baruuk Prime Access is available, the following items have been added to the Prime Vault for a future Prime Resurgence rotation. If you have Relics that contain these items they will remain in your Inventory.","fixes":""},{"name":"Veilbreaker: Revenant Prime: Hotfix 32.0.12","date":"2022-10-12T19:39:20Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1327814-veilbreaker-revenant-prime-hotfix-32012/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Fixed the Theorem Demulcent Arcane applying its weapon damage increase buff to Wisp’s Breach Surge, Baruuk’s Desolate Hands, and Ember’s Fireball. "},{"name":"Veilbreaker: Update 32","date":"2022-09-07T15:00:11Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1321162-veilbreaker-update-32/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Fixed script error with Baruuk’s Serene Storm. "},{"name":"Echoes of the Zariman: Update 31.6","date":"2022-06-09T14:49:52Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1313506-echoes-of-the-zariman-update-316/","additions":"","changes":"Fixed Baruuk being unable to damage Eximus units with his Serene Storm waves.","fixes":""},{"name":"Update 31.5: Angels of the Zariman","date":"2022-04-27T15:02:06Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1305880-update-315-angels-of-the-zariman/","additions":"","changes":"Baruuk’s Lull","fixes":"Fixed Lull not refreshing on normal kills when Client activates Baruuk's Lull ability with the Endless Lullaby equipped. "},{"name":"Echoes of War: Banshee & Mirage Prime Vault: Hotfix 31.1.5","date":"2022-02-17T20:56:48Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1300776-echoes-of-war-banshee-mirage-prime-vault-hotfix-3115/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Fixed Baruuk’s Reactive Storm Augment doing astronomical amounts of damage that ripped through time and space, and would eventually cause him to stop doing damage altogether, as reported here: https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1300588-baruuks-over-damage"},{"name":"Update 31: The New War","date":"2021-12-15T14:23:13Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1290487-update-31-the-new-war/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Fixed Disarming an enemy who is held by Xaku Gaze, Loki Radial Disarm, Baruuk Desolate Hands & Serene Storm, Naramon Disarming Blast, Mag Magnetized Discharge Augment, or Kubrow Neutralize results in them counting as a required kill for mission progress."},{"name":"Update 30.9.0: Prime Resurgence","date":"2021-11-11T13:33:32Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1286070-update-3090-prime-resurgence/","additions":"Lavos, Sevagoth, Xaku, Yareli, Baruuk, Gauss, Hildryn, Wisp, Protea and Grendel are now available and can be used in Frame Fighter once their Fragments have been found/Scanned.","changes":"","fixes":"Fixed the Tenet Agendus’ shield appearing partially upside down when equipped with Baruuk. \nFixed script error with Baruuk’s Desolate hands."},{"name":"Sisters of Parvos: Hotfix 30.5.5","date":"2021-07-29T17:08:32Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1274960-sisters-of-parvos-hotfix-3055/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Baruuk Desolate Hands"},{"name":"Call of the Tempestarii: TennoGen: Update 30.2.0","date":"2021-05-12T19:38:18Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1263575-call-of-the-tempestarii-tennogen-update-3020/","additions":"","changes":"Baruuk Blade of the Lotus Skin by BeastBuster\nBaruuk Zamariu by led2012 & daemonstar","fixes":""},{"name":"Call of the Tempestarii: TennoGen: Update 30.1.0","date":"2021-04-29T17:49:28Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1261802-call-of-the-tempestarii-tennogen-update-3010/","additions":"","changes":"Baruuk Shiraan Skin by Lubox","fixes":""},{"name":"Nightwave: Intermission III: Update 29.7.0","date":"2021-02-01T18:57:32Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1247625-nightwave-intermission-iii-update-2970/","additions":"","changes":"Fixed Baruuk’s Desolate Hands dagger projectile sounds becoming repetitious over time.","fixes":""},{"name":"The Steel Path: Update 28.1.0","date":"2020-07-08T20:09:20Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1205630-the-steel-path-update-2810/","additions":"","changes":"Baruuk Serene Storm","fixes":""},{"name":"Prime Vault: Hotfix 27.5.6 + 27.5.6.1","date":"2020-05-26T18:14:09Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1196415-prime-vault-hotfix-2756-27561/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Fixed Baruuk’s Desolate Hands daggers not fully working with your Companion."},{"name":"Nightwave Series 3: Glassmaker: Hotfix 27.5.5","date":"2020-05-21T14:50:30Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1195171-nightwave-series-3-glassmaker-hotfix-2755/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Fixed a script crash that could occur on Clients if a dagger from Baruuk's Desolate Hands tried to fire at an enemy that was killed immediately."},{"name":"Nightwave Series 3: Glassmaker: Hotfix 27.5.4","date":"2020-05-20T17:29:12Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1194906-nightwave-series-3-glassmaker-hotfix-2754/","additions":"","changes":"Baruuk’s Desolate Hands will no longer consume a charge from Baruuk when sharing with Allies.","fixes":"Fixed inability to target Baruuk’s Desolate Hands and Nezha’s Warding Halo on Defendable objects. "},{"name":"Warframe Revised: Railjack Revisited (Part 1): Update 27.4","date":"2020-05-01T13:21:46Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1189247-warframe-revised-railjack-revisited-part-1-update-274/","additions":"","changes":"Baruuk ","fixes":""},{"name":"Scarlet Spear: 27.3.16","date":"2020-04-22T17:51:40Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1187202-scarlet-spear-27316/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Fixed a script error when loading into a mission and casting Baruuks Lull ability."},{"name":"Scarlet Spear: 27.3.15 + 27.3.15.1","date":"2020-04-17T17:31:25Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1185940-scarlet-spear-27315-273151/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Fixed a script error with Baruuk's Lull ability when used with Railjack Ability Kinesis."},{"name":"Operation: Scarlet Spear: TennoGen 27.3.8 + 27.3.8.1 + 27.3.8.2","date":"2020-04-02T16:33:08Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1181462-operation-scarlet-spear-tennogen-2738-27381-27382/","additions":"","changes":"Baruuk Bedouin Skin by Erneix and Karu","fixes":""},{"name":"Warframe Revised: Update 27.2.0","date":"2020-03-05T15:32:32Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1172454-warframe-revised-update-2720/","additions":"","changes":"Baruuk: 150 to 175\nBaruuk’s Reactive Storm Augment Mod will now also apply its Status Chance and damage type matching to enemy weakness on Serene Storm’s AOE attacks. ","fixes":""},{"name":"Empyrean: Kuva Lich Changes 27.1.0 + 27.1.0.1","date":"2020-02-04T18:58:30Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1166021-empyrean-kuva-lich-changes-2710-27101/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Fixed Baruuk’s Reactive Storm Augment resetting the Status Chance back to non-Augmented values after a direct punch to someone."},{"name":"Rising Tide: Hotfix 26.1.3","date":"2019-11-26T19:33:56Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1146782-rising-tide-hotfix-2613/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Fixed a crash when using Baruuk’s Desert Wind's Heavy Attack."},{"name":"Rising Tide: Hotfix 26.1.2","date":"2019-11-25T21:20:27Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1146388-rising-tide-hotfix-2612/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Fixed a script error when casting Baruuk’s Serene Storm ability."},{"name":"The Old Blood: Hotfix 26.0.3","date":"2019-11-01T20:41:07Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1137487-the-old-blood-hotfix-2603/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Fixed missing sounds for Baruuk’s Desert Wind."},{"name":"Saint of Altra: Update 25.7.0","date":"2019-08-29T21:35:56Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1123841-saint-of-altra-update-2570/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Fixed Baruuk taking much longer to deploy Spectres. \nFixed Baruuk’s Meroe helmet tassel sometimes disappearing when viewing his diorama at certain angles. "},{"name":"The Jovian Concord: Hotfix 25.2.3","date":"2019-06-25T18:04:46Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1105676-the-jovian-concord-hotfix-2523/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Fixed Baruuk’s Desolate Hands charge indicator not updating for Clients after Transferring to the Operator. "},{"name":"Plains of Eidolon Remaster: Hotfix 24.6.2 + 24.6.2.1","date":"2019-04-05T20:50:12Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1080295-plains-of-eidolon-remaster-hotfix-2462-24621/","additions":"","changes":"Fixed the sleep abilities of Ivara, Baruuk, and Equinox not giving you the option to capture animals in Plains of Eidolon.","fixes":""},{"name":"Plains of Eidolon Remaster: Update 24.6.0","date":"2019-04-04T23:14:14Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1079621-plains-of-eidolon-remaster-update-2460/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Fixed some effects in Baruuk's Restraint UI not correctly lining up as the meter fills up."},{"name":"Buried Debts: Hotfix 24.4.1","date":"2019-03-08T05:01:21Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1067531-buried-debts-hotfix-2441/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Fixed Baruuk's Desert Wind slam attack not working. Slam attack now always pushes enemies away (would previously pull if you were parrying)."},{"name":"Buried Debts: Update 24.4.0","date":"2019-03-08T02:01:23Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1067397-buried-debts-update-2440/","additions":"","changes":"Respective Ability videos now also appear upon hover-over to add that little extra spice! This initial Ability video aspect is currently functional for Excalibur, Mag, Volt, Garuda, Baruuk, Revenant, and Hildryn! More to gradually come!\nMelee combo damage multiplier now affects Baruuk Desert Wind waves.\nImproved the camera shake on Baruuk’s Serene Storm ability.","fixes":"Fixed Baruuk’s Restraint amount changing following a Host migration for Clients.\nFixed glitchy textures in Baruuk’s diorama."},{"name":"Fortuna: Hotfix 24.2.9 + 24.2.9.1","date":"2019-01-18T14:16:39Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1055092-fortuna-hotfix-2429-24291/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Fixed Baruuk’s Restraint meter not maintaining after a Host migration. We’re continuing to investigate the issue still occurring for Clients.\nFixed Baruuk’s Restraint UI particles not appearing when the HUD Scale is increased. "},{"name":"Fortuna: Hotfix 24.2.8","date":"2019-01-15T14:46:54Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1054314-fortuna-hotfix-2428/","additions":"","changes":"Baruuk’s Elude conal indicator FX will now only be seen by the local player (person casting the ability). \nSlight tweak to Baruuk’s Elude ability FX that unnecessarily pulsed.\nFixed using Transference while Baruuk’s Savagery is active resulting in breaking his custom UI.","fixes":""},{"name":"Fortuna: Hotfix 24.2.7 + 24.2.7.1","date":"2019-01-09T18:37:18Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1052727-fortuna-hotfix-2427-24271/","additions":"","changes":"Baruuk’s end of Elude animation no longer prevents movement.\nImprovements towards performance/visual issues with Baruuk's Elude ability by removing the blur FX if using the ‘Low Particle Quality’ setting based on feedback:\nReduced the FX density of Baruuk’s Lull fog to fix reported performance issues. \nFixed Baruuk’s Desert Wind weapon displaying as having Impact, Puncture, and Slash in the Arsenal when it's just Impact.\nFixed Baruuk’s Serene Storm Desert Wind waves not hitting ragdolled enemies.\nFixed Baruuk’s Serene Storm Desert Wind waves not matching FX direction.\nFixed a script error when casting Baruuk’s Serene Storm ability.\nFixed a script error when casting Baruuk’s Desolate Hands ability.","fixes":""},{"name":"Fortuna: Hotfix 24.2.5","date":"2018-12-20T00:45:07Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1046112-fortuna-hotfix-2425/","additions":"","changes":"Animals will be less stressed the closer you are to them when casting Baruuk’s Lull ability.","fixes":""},{"name":"Fortuna: Mesa Prime - Hotfix 24.2.3","date":"2018-12-19T15:53:01Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1045817-fortuna-mesa-prime-hotfix-2423/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Fixed a script error that could occur if you died and revived shortly after casting Baruuk's Lull, resulting in affected enemies being permanently asleep."},{"name":"Fortuna: Mesa Prime - Hotfix 24.2.2","date":"2018-12-18T18:58:36Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1045159-fortuna-mesa-prime-hotfix-2422/","additions":"","changes":"","fixes":"Fixed inability to edit the Baruuk Mandala Decoration after placing it.\nFixed Baruuk’s [PH] NOT EDGY ENOUGH UI text."},{"name":"Fortuna: The Profit-Taker - Update 24.2","date":"2018-12-18T13:59:14Z","url":"https://forums.warframe.com/topic/1044890-fortuna-the-profit-taker-update-242/","additions":"A new Baruuk UI Theme and Stalker UI Theme are now purchasable under Options > Interface > UI Customization. ","changes":"","fixes":""}],"wikiAvailable":true,"aura":"naramon","conclave":false,"color":0,"introduced":{"name":"Hotfix 32.2.5","url":"https://wiki.warframe.com/w/Update_32%23Hotfix_32.2.5","aliases":["32.2.5"],"parent":"32.0","date":"2022-12-14"},"polarities":["naramon","vazarin","madurai"],"sex":"Male","sprint":1.2,"wikiaUrl":"https://wiki.warframe.com/w/Baruuk%2FPrime","releaseDate":"2022-12-14","isPrime":true,"vaulted":true,"vaultDate":"2024-11-13","estimatedVaultDate":"2024-11-13","masterable":true}